data.text: @etnow Etm she's not a princess, she's a duchess...duh.

@etnow If only she would quit the “messy bun” which really isn’t so much a messy bun as it is her plotting and selecting which pieces of hair to pull out of her bun to make it appear messy...a.k.a. trying way too hard to make it appear a messy bun - it just looks contrived and not good
@etnow Correction:  Meghan is a duchess, not a princess.  As a commoner wed to a royal, I don't believe she qualifies for the princess title.
